	measure 'Total VendasYTD' = ```
			
			    TOTALYTD(
			        [Total Vendas],
			        'Tabela Calendário'[Date]
			    )
			```
		formatString: "R$"\ #,0.###############;-"R$"\ #,0.###############;"R$"\ #,0.###############
